meta {
  name: POST climatisation start
  type: http
  seq: 6
}

post {
  url: {{base_url}}/vehicle/v1/vehicles/{{vin}}/climatisation/start-stop
  body: json
  auth: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{access_token}}
}

headers {
  Content-Type: application/json
  Accept: application/json
}

body:json {
  {
    "action": "start"
  }
}

docs {
  v1.8.8 (Session 3B) — combined endpoint primary. On 404 falls back to
  /vehicle/v1/vehicles/{vin}/climatisation/start with body
  {"targetTemperature": 21.0, "targetTemperatureUnit": "celsius",
   "climatisationWithoutExternalPower": true, "windowHeatingEnabled": true}.

  v1.14.0 (#29 PPE/PPC Klima) — Audi Q6/A6 e-tron + RS e-tron GT
  Facelift + A3 2024+ PHEV require new body shape:
    {"climatisationMode": "comfort",
     "climatisationWithoutExternalPower": true,
     "windowHeatingEnabled": true}
  (NO targetTemperature). User opts in via CONF_FORCE_PPE_CLIMATE.

  Implementation: VWEUClient.command_start_climate(vin, ppe_mode=False)
  in cariad/api/vw_eu.py:258. Audi inherits.
}
